{"tid":1160294,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"他們曾說過……","createTime":"2019-05-18T11:17:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-18T11:17:14.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1a6d2b703e6c2260ba90783fba20814d7bddfb30","tid":1160294,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T11:17:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190518/20681125\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190518%2F20681125&d=vM7vEUXlfhstYrouAjV2fiZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=ca38afbe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190518%2F20681125&h=a1ffb0d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190518/20681125</a><br />\n<br />\n他們曾說過&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190518/large/a1002a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190518%2Flarge%2Fa1002a.gif&h=a038d701&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1989年5月，北京各界紛紛上街聲援絕食學生。<br />\n<br />\n舉着「立即對話，刻不容緩」、「求民主無損國家形象」等矚目橫額的民主黨派人士，高呼口號走過廣場，當打着「慈悲為懷愛人如己」的首都佛教徒慰問隊走過來的時候，四周響起了熱烈的掌聲。<br />\n<br />\n中國人民銀行總行的遊行隧伍經過人民大會堂東門時，不斷呼喊：「不給官倒貸款！」「凍結官倒帳戶！」海關總署的聲援隊伍喊道：「官倒走私，鐵證如山！」受到周圍學生、群眾熱烈鼓掌歡迎。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;1989年今天，《人民日報》發表以題為〈首都各界百餘萬人遊行 聲援絕食請願的大學生 強烈要求立即對話救人救國〉的頭條報道。  <br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：六四30年：下次六四很快來臨 王丹 王軍濤<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n六四30年：下次六四很快來臨 王丹 王軍濤<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n港故事：金茶王大師傅 半世紀 真功夫"}]}